      "content": "it just feels like the \"green tech jobs\" thing is kind of a hollow promise when you compare it to the actual, proven jobs we have now. isn't it kind of unfair to say it's \"resilient\" when it's basically just killing off an industry that's been the backbone of pa for a long time? feels like the state is just picking winners and losers based on a trend.",
